# CMake & Dependencies

- Require **CMake 3.16+** and set the C++17 standard explicitly.
- Single executable target: `urlmon`. Call `enable_testing()` for ctest.
- Find libcurl with `find_package(CURL REQUIRED)` and link `CURL::libcurl`.
- Pull `yaml-cpp` and `nlohmann/json` via `FetchContent` with **pinned version
  tags** — never a branch or floating ref.

```cmake
# GOOD: pinned, reproducible
FetchContent_Declare(
  yaml-cpp
  GIT_REPOSITORY https://github.com/jbeder/yaml-cpp.git
  GIT_TAG 0.8.0            # pinned tag, not master
)

# BAD: floating ref — build is not reproducible
FetchContent_Declare(
  json
  GIT_REPOSITORY https://github.com/nlohmann/json.git
  GIT_TAG master
)
```
